{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, improving generative AIs should be accompanied by an effective design of human-AI interactions that promote users' cognitive activities for critical decision-making or opinion formulation.",
    "In this study, we proposed a novel human-chatbot interaction strategy, suggestive ending, for generative AI-powered chatbot answers to foster decision-making from various perspectives.",
    "Our method is inspired by the cliffhanger ending narrative technique, which ends a story without specifying conclusions to spark readers' curiosity as to what will happen next.",
    "The cliffhanger method is often used in television series.",
    "It relates to a psychological phenomenon known as the Ovsiankina effect, where humans are often urged to finish the uncompleted tasks they have initiated (Wirz et al., 2023)."
  ]
}